1. *Leta* se nad oblacima. (It flies above the clouds.)
2. Leptir leta po cvetu. (The butterfly is flying over the flower.)
3. Ptica *leta* brzo. (The bird is flying fast.)
4. Deca se igraju i *lete* po dvori≈°tu. (The children are playing and running around the yard.)
5. Letim u Njujork za praznike. (I'm flying to New York for the holidays.)